reviewText: 2013 will go down as a season to remember and I will always remember kick Bama kick. Sure we fell short of winnng the national championship but we went from 0-8 to winning the sec. And watching chris Davis run the missed field goal back for the game winning touchdown against the over rated tide was great Auburn 34 crappy tide 28

...if any Auburn football fan is reading this review, you are a buying customer. You know you need it! You know you want it!

For a anyone else, strap on your seatbelts and prepare for Toad's wild ride....
